        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنْ سَرَّهُ أَنْ يَكْثُرَ خَيْرُ بَيْتِهِ فَلْيَتَوَضَّأْ عِنْدَ حُضُورِ طَعَامِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4264 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said: \"Whoever desires that the blessings of his house increase, let him perform ablution when food is brought.\""
        ]
